WEBVTT

01:51.200 --> 01:53.400
To open a spacetime rift spanning 50 years

01:54.200 --> 01:56.320
requires me to disperse
all of my cultivation

01:56.840 --> 01:59.000
and transform into a demon form.

02:01.400 --> 02:03.640
And maintaining the rift will inflict

02:03.720 --> 02:06.240
continuous, severe damage
on the spellcaster.

02:07.160 --> 02:09.880
Lu Wuyi went on continuous rewinds
with Lonescale's power.

02:10.560 --> 02:13.840
The Oracle Stone has provided her
with endless power,

02:13.920 --> 02:16.160
but she's still heavily wounded.

02:17.360 --> 02:18.720
So, this time,

02:19.400 --> 02:20.920
Li Jie,

02:22.280 --> 02:23.120
you have to do it.

02:24.960 --> 02:25.800
Hua Qi.

02:25.880 --> 02:28.040
You must keep healing him

02:28.120 --> 02:29.920
with the method of purification.

02:30.440 --> 02:33.840
Otherwise, he won't be able
to bear the pain of maintaining the rift.

02:40.560 --> 02:41.600
Mo Yuntan.

02:41.680 --> 02:45.240
Your formation
can withstand spell attacks.

02:45.920 --> 02:47.440
Keep them safe.

02:48.560 --> 02:51.000
Shiguang. You will deal with Jiu Ying.

02:51.080 --> 02:53.960
You're the last dragon in the world.

02:54.040 --> 02:56.640
I hope you save the world.

03:12.080 --> 03:16.320
Leave the rewind to me.

03:18.080 --> 03:20.240
Lu Wuyi is my fated one.

03:21.120 --> 03:23.080
If she is doomed to perish,

03:23.840 --> 03:25.280
then I shall be the one

03:26.520 --> 03:28.520
who brings everything to an end.

03:33.840 --> 03:36.240
You must create another exit

03:36.320 --> 03:38.680
with your own strength in the rift.

03:40.000 --> 03:44.280
I'll maintain the exit here
with all my remaining power.

03:44.360 --> 03:46.280
Make it quick.

03:47.360 --> 03:49.280
If you can't return in time,

03:49.880 --> 03:51.800
you'll be trapped in the rift

03:51.880 --> 03:53.520
and taken to the unknown.

03:54.680 --> 03:58.200
You may even cease to exist.

04:28.160 --> 04:29.120
Come on.

04:29.840 --> 04:32.360
A constant stream of fear and despair.

04:32.880 --> 04:35.160
Wu Shiguang. How are you going to beat me?

05:19.040 --> 05:22.200
With your twin blades unsheathed,

05:23.240 --> 05:27.200
this empty chest of yours
is as vulnerable as a sheet of paper.

05:53.160 --> 05:54.520
Hua Qi, don't be distracted.

05:54.600 --> 05:56.040
Keep healing Li Jie.

06:36.920 --> 06:37.880
The earthquake

06:39.200 --> 06:40.080
stopped.

06:42.480 --> 06:45.800
Wu Wangyan is still so silly.

06:46.920 --> 06:48.040
What did you say?

06:49.360 --> 06:51.800
Why do you think
the Four-Pillar Formation stopped?

06:53.520 --> 06:55.680
Because they sacrificed themselves.

07:55.520 --> 07:56.560
Jin Zheng.

08:51.480 --> 08:53.360
My soul I devote.

08:54.400 --> 08:55.560
Long live the dragon.

08:55.640 --> 08:57.240
Mo Yuntan. No!

09:22.800 --> 09:24.800
You annoying junior.

09:26.560 --> 09:28.320
Hurry up and become a double-flower.

09:29.160 --> 09:31.960
Congratulations on becoming
a double-flower.

09:39.800 --> 09:41.040
Cherish me.

09:41.120 --> 09:43.200
Only I would call you Senior.

10:07.440 --> 10:10.120
You must create another exit

10:10.200 --> 10:12.560
with your own strength in the rift.

10:13.080 --> 10:16.480
Although you have
the Dragon Deity's Power of Chi Wen,

10:17.080 --> 10:19.240
you can't reach
the realm of the six-flower yet.

10:20.600 --> 10:21.920
Just do your best.

12:44.880 --> 12:47.120
Wrathful sandstorm.

12:54.720 --> 12:56.280
Eastern Purple Lightning.

12:56.880 --> 12:58.600
Searing flames.

12:59.240 --> 13:00.880
By the fox's call.

13:01.720 --> 13:03.560
Rewind of Sun and Moon.

13:12.040 --> 13:13.800
Grant me your power.

13:17.880 --> 13:19.080
Master Ji Ling.

13:19.800 --> 13:21.080
From now on,

13:21.920 --> 13:23.240
you're on your own.

13:27.640 --> 13:29.440
Come!

14:34.840 --> 14:36.960
How dare you trespass
into the Formless Moon?

14:37.800 --> 14:39.120
Who are you?

14:46.520 --> 14:48.440
The man who came to take your life.

16:22.040 --> 16:23.160
Ji Ling.

16:32.160 --> 16:33.320
Where is Ji Ling?

16:34.360 --> 16:35.400
Lu Wuyi.

17:09.119 --> 17:10.560
Use the Guili Sword

17:11.599 --> 17:13.160
and the Dragon Deity's Power

17:14.359 --> 17:16.800
to destroy the last shard
of the Oracle Stone.

17:17.839 --> 17:19.119
Only then

17:21.960 --> 17:24.280
can you kill Jiu Ying for good.

17:25.359 --> 17:27.400
But you'll also die.

17:35.160 --> 17:37.160
I was never supposed to exist.

17:42.560 --> 17:43.720
Wu Shiguang.

17:45.760 --> 17:47.400
Tell Wangyan

17:50.720 --> 17:52.320
that I miss her.

18:46.480 --> 18:48.600
No.

18:49.160 --> 18:51.640
You're dying with me.

19:07.000 --> 19:07.880
Ji Ling.

19:37.560 --> 19:38.640
Ji Ling.

19:41.360 --> 19:42.920
I'm coming to you.

19:44.640 --> 19:45.920
Don't cry.

19:46.440 --> 19:47.760
Ji…

19:47.840 --> 19:48.880
Don't cry.

19:49.800 --> 19:51.440
I'll wait for you over there.

19:52.760 --> 19:55.680
I'll pick you up with a bundle of flowers.

19:57.000 --> 19:59.000
A huge bundle.

20:00.560 --> 20:01.600
This way,

20:03.240 --> 20:05.240
you won't be afraid.

20:07.320 --> 20:09.840
Remember to pick me up with flowers.

20:12.320 --> 20:14.680
I want a huge bundle of flowers.

21:40.080 --> 21:41.360
Who are you?

21:48.040 --> 21:49.400
Where am I?

21:58.920 --> 22:00.240
Are you also

22:01.720 --> 22:03.160
going to kill me?

22:07.400 --> 22:09.120
I've been looking for you.

22:10.560 --> 22:12.000
I'll take you home.

22:18.760 --> 22:19.920
I'm scared.

22:22.200 --> 22:23.280
Of me?

22:30.440 --> 22:31.760
Of this place.

22:32.360 --> 22:33.440
It's so dark

22:34.560 --> 22:35.560
and so cold.

22:38.200 --> 22:40.320
But I don't know why

22:42.880 --> 22:44.240
I feel at ease

22:46.040 --> 22:47.560
looking at you.

23:01.480 --> 23:03.000
Then just look at me.

23:04.000 --> 23:04.840
This way,

23:05.720 --> 23:07.320
you won't be afraid.

23:11.320 --> 23:13.280
I think I'm really not afraid anymore.

23:18.560 --> 23:20.200
What's your name?

23:23.800 --> 23:24.800
My name

23:28.240 --> 23:29.080
is Ji Ling.

23:31.040 --> 23:32.920
"Ji" as in "a temporary lodging".

23:34.160 --> 23:35.920
"Ling" as in "hearts connected".

23:42.080 --> 23:44.160
Ji Ling.

23:48.280 --> 23:49.680
I'll remember it.

24:04.440 --> 24:05.400
Go to sleep.

24:54.360 --> 24:55.240
Li Jie.

24:58.640 --> 24:59.760
Master Dragon Deity.

25:05.720 --> 25:06.840
Master Dragon Deity.

25:08.760 --> 25:09.760
Master Dragon Deity.

25:09.840 --> 25:11.160
We did it.

25:12.160 --> 25:13.520
We did it.

25:14.600 --> 25:16.280
-Master Dragon Deity.
-We did it.

25:17.480 --> 25:18.520
Thank you.

25:19.880 --> 25:21.080
Thank you all.

25:23.400 --> 25:24.240
Thank you.

25:53.240 --> 25:54.120
Don't be sad.

25:55.360 --> 25:57.920
Maybe they just went to another world.

25:59.920 --> 26:01.200
Or perhaps,

26:01.800 --> 26:04.720
Ji Ling chose to stay
in the spacetime rift.

26:05.520 --> 26:07.760
I bet he didn't want to come back

26:09.000 --> 26:11.600
to this world where Lu Wuyi never existed.

26:30.520 --> 26:31.480
Wu Wangyan.

26:32.400 --> 26:33.360
You Chi.

26:34.760 --> 26:35.800
Wu Wangyan.

27:36.320 --> 27:38.280
I always called you a coward

27:39.400 --> 27:40.840
who runs away from danger.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.680
Why didn't you run?

27:49.120 --> 27:50.520
Why didn't you run?

27:51.400 --> 27:53.000
Why didn't you run?

29:05.880 --> 29:07.080
Wu Shiguang.

29:09.400 --> 29:10.640
In this life,

29:12.480 --> 29:14.040
I can't repay

29:17.840 --> 29:19.240
your deep affection.

29:21.640 --> 29:22.760
If there is an afterlife,

29:24.000 --> 29:25.880
I swear I will find you.

29:42.560 --> 29:44.280
Please save my sister.

32:19.680 --> 32:20.880
Are you scared?

32:25.200 --> 32:26.200
No.

33:48.000 --> 33:49.520
Morning, Master Dragon Deity.

33:52.160 --> 33:53.200
Master Dragon Deity.

33:56.600 --> 33:57.640
Wu Shiguang.

33:59.400 --> 34:00.840
What are you doing here?

34:52.719 --> 34:53.719
What's wrong?

35:03.240 --> 35:04.920
What happened to your face?

35:06.320 --> 35:07.760
Got into a fight again?

35:12.400 --> 35:13.920
I've been busy these days.

35:15.160 --> 35:17.080
Being a commander of the Shilin Sect

35:17.160 --> 35:19.080
is harder than I thought.

35:19.160 --> 35:21.200
But Father always said,

35:21.760 --> 35:23.560
"Do your best."

35:27.000 --> 35:28.240
Work harder.

35:31.680 --> 35:35.160
You've always been such a crybaby.

35:35.240 --> 35:37.200
You're the Master Dragon Deity now.

35:37.280 --> 35:39.600
You can't be
that scared little boy anymore.

36:03.480 --> 36:05.640
What's wrong? Had a nightmare?

36:07.760 --> 36:08.600
No.

36:10.560 --> 36:12.080
It was a sweet dream.

36:18.280 --> 36:19.840
But then I woke up.

36:21.920 --> 36:23.600
So, I'm a bit upset.

36:26.440 --> 36:28.040
I came to tell you

36:28.680 --> 36:30.960
that the Oracle Stone gave a new prophecy.

36:33.240 --> 36:34.200
The old dragon falls.

36:34.720 --> 36:35.920
The new dragon rises.

36:36.000 --> 36:37.840
Rewind the river of time.

36:38.480 --> 36:39.880
A new chapter has started.

36:49.480 --> 36:51.120
-Master Dragon Deity.
-We pray for your blessings.

36:51.200 --> 36:52.560
Master Dragon Deity, please…

36:52.640 --> 36:54.080
-Please grant my wishes.
-Master Dragon Deity…

36:57.360 --> 36:59.120
ALL FLOURISH FOR THE SCALES

36:59.200 --> 37:01.560
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

37:01.640 --> 37:03.400
You've become the Master Dragon Deity.

37:04.160 --> 37:05.200
I have to work harder

37:06.160 --> 37:08.960
to be a great hero
and honor our ancestors.

37:14.960 --> 37:16.880
You're already a great hero.

37:19.600 --> 37:20.480
Again?

37:21.080 --> 37:22.200
Father once said,

37:23.240 --> 37:24.320
"Be down to earth.

37:25.000 --> 37:26.480
Stop daydreaming."

37:40.920 --> 37:41.920
Miss Mu Long.

37:45.200 --> 37:47.320
You came to offer incense too?

37:49.360 --> 37:51.600
I finished my book.

37:52.440 --> 37:54.120
Want to read it?

37:55.560 --> 37:56.960
O-Of course.

37:57.040 --> 37:58.160
I want to be your first…

38:00.920 --> 38:02.080
first reader.

38:05.280 --> 38:07.080
TALES TOLD BY MU, MU LONG

38:26.760 --> 38:28.520
Brother. Do you have any coins?

38:28.600 --> 38:32.280
Can I get a coin
for the Pond of Merit to make a wish?

38:40.160 --> 38:42.600
Master Dragon Deity will keep blessing us.

38:43.680 --> 38:45.080
Look, a double-flower hunter.

38:45.160 --> 38:46.960
I saw a double-flower hunter.

38:47.040 --> 38:48.960
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

38:53.800 --> 38:55.760
I saw a double-flower hunter.

38:55.840 --> 38:58.040
The middle one has one more flower.

38:58.120 --> 38:59.320
Triple-flower.

38:59.400 --> 39:00.640
Triple-flower.

39:00.720 --> 39:01.960
Come and see!

39:02.480 --> 39:03.920
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:04.000 --> 39:05.680
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:05.760 --> 39:07.560
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:07.640 --> 39:09.000
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:09.080 --> 39:10.960
Master Dragon Deity has manifested.

39:19.720 --> 39:20.680
Ji Ling.

39:21.520 --> 39:22.520
Do you see it?

39:23.640 --> 39:26.360
It's the wonderful world
you died to protect.

39:28.640 --> 39:30.280
I'll keep guarding it.

39:31.640 --> 39:33.360
As long as there are dragons,

39:34.240 --> 39:37.480
the light of faith
will not be extinguished.

39:51.120 --> 39:52.320
Wu Wangyan.

40:11.120 --> 40:12.240
You are…

40:40.120 --> 40:42.480
Why do you have my hair?

40:50.600 --> 40:51.840
That is

40:54.040 --> 40:57.560
a long story to be told.

41:23.440 --> 41:24.640
Once,

41:24.720 --> 41:27.200
I thought the mission was everything,

41:27.880 --> 41:31.160
but I never thought that the mission
would come to an end.

41:32.240 --> 41:34.360
Maybe it's time to let go

41:34.880 --> 41:37.240
and see the world out there.

41:38.880 --> 41:41.560
Maybe I'll figure out who I am

41:42.280 --> 41:44.360
and the meaning of my existence.

41:45.200 --> 41:47.640
And this is probably the answer

41:48.200 --> 41:49.760
all of us

41:50.280 --> 41:52.240
are seeking our entire lives.

41:53.920 --> 41:54.880
Come and find me.

41:57.960 --> 42:01.360
And I think there is a voice

42:01.440 --> 42:03.280
telling me to find someone.

42:03.360 --> 42:05.600
But I don't know
where to find that person.

42:05.680 --> 42:08.160
I don't even know his name.

42:12.960 --> 42:15.800
MOONLIGHT OVER THE WASTELAND
SCALES BLESS ALL CREATURES

42:15.880 --> 42:18.680
GORGEOUS AS A DREAM
FATE'S PATHS CONVERGE

42:28.120 --> 42:30.600
Demons coming!

42:30.680 --> 42:33.320
Demons coming!

42:33.400 --> 42:35.280
-Here to catch you.
-Be careful.

42:35.360 --> 42:36.320
Come here.

42:37.520 --> 42:39.880
There are no demons in the world.

42:39.960 --> 42:43.400
Those are stories adults made up
to scare the kids.

42:43.480 --> 42:45.600
How boring.

42:45.680 --> 42:48.040
It would be so much fun

42:48.120 --> 42:49.440
if there were demons.

42:50.600 --> 42:51.440
Here.

42:51.960 --> 42:54.480
Demons coming!

42:54.560 --> 42:56.160
Demons coming to catch you!

42:56.240 --> 42:57.720
Demons coming to catch you!

42:58.240 --> 42:59.320
Demons coming!

42:59.840 --> 43:01.080
Here to catch you!

43:01.160 --> 43:06.600
PETALS AND GREENS

44:04.320 --> 44:05.960
Young Miss, do you like flowers?

44:10.640 --> 44:11.480
Yes, I do.

44:12.560 --> 44:13.480
Would you like some?

44:16.720 --> 44:18.400
All fresh. I just picked them.

44:20.880 --> 44:21.720
I…

44:23.360 --> 44:24.360
have no money.

44:29.640 --> 44:31.440
I'm just a worker here.

44:31.960 --> 44:33.720
If I were the boss,

44:34.400 --> 44:36.120
I would give you some.

44:36.200 --> 44:37.760
What should I do?

44:38.800 --> 44:39.960
No need.

44:40.480 --> 44:42.920
You don't have to do this. Thank you.

45:01.640 --> 45:02.520
Young Miss.

45:24.080 --> 45:25.120
Here.

45:38.720 --> 45:40.600
You… You don't want them?

45:41.440 --> 45:44.440
I picked these raspberries
by the lake near home.

45:44.520 --> 45:47.080
Do… Do you like raspberries?

46:16.880 --> 46:17.920
So sweet.
